		{
			"type": "action",
			"name": "Third Eye",
			"system": {
				"actionType": {
					"value": "action"
				},
				"description": {
					"value": "<p>The chort focuses its third Eye upon a creature it can see within 60 feet. Target creature must attempt at a @Check[will|dc:26] save or be affected randomly by one of the following effects (chosen before the saving throw).</p><hr /><ol><li><p><em><strong>Sleep</strong>:</em> Target creature is considered as if under the effect of a @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.o4lRVTwSxnOOn5vl]{Sleep} spell casted as a 5th-rank primal spell.</p></li><li><p><em><strong>Panic</strong></em><strong>:</strong> Target creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Frightened 2} (if they critically fails they're also @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.sDPxOjQ9kx2RZE8D]{Fleeing} for 1 round).</p></li><li><p><strong>S</strong><em><strong>icken</strong></em>: Target creature is Sicken 1 (@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.fesd1n5eVhpCSS18]{Sickened 2} with a critical failure).</p></li></ol><p></p>",
